OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FOne of Mexico's most notorious drug
OL,7,Flords "El Mencho" was killed in a
OL,8,Fmilitary operation on Sunday in
OL,9,FTapalpa, sparking widespread
OL,10,Fretaliatory violence
OL,12,FThe death of one man has triggered
OL,13,Fviolent protests across Mexico. More
OL,14,Fthan 70 people have died, sparking
OL,15,Fstrict travel warnings for tourists
OL,16,Fand casting doubt over this summer's
OL,17,FWorld Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
