OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772067788
OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FOn Sunday, El Mencho - Mexico's most
OL,7,Fwanted man - and ten of his
OL,8,Facquaintances were killed during a
OL,9,Fmilitary operation in the state of
OL,10,FJalisco.
OL,12,FMexican Authorities have now said
OL,13,Fsurveillance of one of El Mencho's
OL,14,Fromantic partners led armed forces in
OL,15,Fthe direction of the cartel leader.
OL,17,FHis death triggered chaos in the
OL,18,Fcountry, with vehicles set ablaze
OL,19,Facross the state, including in the
OL,20,Ftourist hot spots of Guadalajara and
OL,21,FPuerto Vallarta.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772067788
OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FMexico Security Secretary Omar Garcia
OL,7,FHarfuch said 25 members of the
OL,8,FNational Guard were killed in Jalisco
OL,9,Fin six separate attacks. He also said
OL,10,F30 criminal suspects were killed in
OL,11,FJalisco and four others were killed in
OL,12,FMichoacan.
OL,14,FThe violence has prompted new fears
OL,15,Fover this summer's World Cup. Two top-
OL,16,Fflight fixtures in Mexico have already
OL,17,Fbeen postponed due to the violence.
OL,19,FWho is El Mencho?
OL,26,@nD@drttD@Hrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
