PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772067788
OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FIn 2020, the cartel carried out a
OL,7,Fspectacular assassination attempt with
OL,8,Fgrenades and high-powered rifles in
OL,9,Fthe heart of Mexico City against the
OL,10,Fthen-head of the capital's police
OL,11,Fforce and now federal security
OL,12,Fsecretary.
OL,14,FFollowing a romantic partner - how was
OL,15,FEl Mencho finally caught?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
