OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FAccording to the country's defence
OL,7,Fsecretary, General Ricardo Trevilla
OL,8,FTrejo, the military began an operation
OL,9,Fto arrest El Mencho, after which a
OL,10,F"very violent clash" between cartel
OL,11,Fmembers and Mexican special forces
OL,12,Fensued.
OL,14,FAfter years of unsuccessful attempts,
OL,15,Fmilitary investigators successfully
OL,16,Fidentified a trusted associate of one
OL,17,Fof the cartel leader's romantic
OL,18,Fpartners.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772067788
OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FThat individual escorted the woman to
OL,7,FTapalpa, Jalisco, for a meeting with
OL,8,FEl Mencho. Trevilla confirmed this
OL,9,Finformation with US intelligence
OL,10,Fhelped pinpoint an exact location.
OL,12,FGiven fresh hope, the Mexican Army
OL,13,Flaunched their ground operation to
OL,14,Fcapture him in Tapalpa, troops came
OL,15,Funder fire and killed eight people at
OL,16,Fthe location.
OL,18,FThree more people, including El
OL,19,FMencho, were wounded and later died,
OL,20,Faccording to the country's defense
OL,21,Fsecretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
