OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FJalisco's capital, Guadalajara, was
OL,7,Fturned into a ghost town Sunday night
OL,8,Fas civilians sheltered. School was
OL,9,Fcanceled on Monday in several states.
OL,11,FAuthorities in Jalisco, Michoacan, and
OL,12,FGuanajuato reported at least 14 dead,
OL,13,Fincluding seven National Guard troops.
OL,15,FPuerto Vallarta International Airport
OL,16,Fannounced it had cancelled "all
OL,17,Finternational operations and most of
OL,18,Fthe domestic flights" on Sunday local
OL,19,Ftime.
OL,26,@sD@`rpxD@\OUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
