OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FThe UK's warnings were echoed by the
OL,7,FUnited States Embassy in Mexico, which
OL,8,Furged Americans to "shelter in place".
OL,10,FBritons were also advised to monitor
OL,11,Flocal media and follow guidance from
OL,12,Fauthorities.
OL,14,F"If you do decide to travel, we
OL,15,Frecommend intercity road travel during
OL,16,Fdaylight hours," the official advice
OL,17,Fread.
OL,19,FLess than four months away, how will
OL,20,Fthe World Cup be affected?
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@eO]vD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
