OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FMexico is one of three host countries
OL,7,Ffor the 2026 World Cup, alongside
OL,8,FCanada and the US. Guadalajara is one
OL,9,Fof Mexico's three host cities, along
OL,10,Fwith Mexico City and Monterrey.
OL,12,FIt is almost unprecedented for such
OL,13,Flevels of violence to occur in a host
OL,14,Fcity, just months before fans from
OL,15,Faround the world are due to visit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772067788
OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FLiga MX, Mexico's equivalent to the
OL,7,FPremier League, has already postponed
OL,8,Fone match since El Mencho's death
OL,9,Fbetween Queretaro and FC Juarez. In
OL,10,Fthe Liga MX Femenil, the women's top
OL,11,Fflight, the game between Guadalajara
OL,12,Fand America was also postponed. Both
OL,13,Fdue to security fears.
OL,15,FDespite Queretaro's postponement, the
OL,16,FMexico national team continue to train
OL,17,Fat the club ahead of Wednesday's
OL,18,Ffriendly against Iceland. Credit:
OL,19,FInstagram / @miseleccionmx
OL,26,@qD@MrrqD@\rptD@GrrwD@Mrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
