OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772067788
OL,3,CHow Mexican drug lord's death has cast
OL,4,Cdoubt on the World Cup
OL,6,FGuadalajara is due to host a match on
OL,7,Fthe opening night of the tournament,
OL,8,Fas well as the highly anticipated
OL,9,Fgroup stage match between Uruguay and
OL,10,FSpain.
OL,12,FNeither England nor Scotland will be
OL,13,Fplaying any of their matches in
OL,14,FGuadalajara. However, they could play
OL,15,Fin Mexico City should they reach the
OL,16,Fknockouts.
OL,18,FNo new travel guidance has been issued
OL,19,Ffor the tournament in response to the
OL,20,Flatest unrest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
